snippet.textDisplay:
OMG you picked an AWESOME two liter factory turbo rally king engined car. This engine is the real deal from the 1990s World Rally days along with Mitsubishi 4G63 (factory turbo 2 liter) and Subaru EJ20 (factory turbo 2 liter). I think SKODA and FORD were the only other competitors of merit but you got a rear engine car with the rally engine! SWEEEEET. I can't wait. This car's engine is more likely to be overbuilt and undertuned in its stock config, so I am betting it will not go POP like the Corolla you put in that Yaris which wasn't intended for high power, as we discovered.
I hope you also work on handling with sway bars and big brakes. This lightweight rear engine car can be FAST on a road circuit.
